# colorSteps

.Synopsis
Create a list of intermediate colors between two colors.

.Syntax

.Types

.Function
`list[Color] colorSteps(Color from, Color to, int steps)`

.Details

.Description
Create a list of interpolated colors between `from` and `to` in a given number of `steps`.

.Examples
[source,rascal-figure,width=,height=,file=h1.png]
----
                boxes = [ box([size(50), fillColor(c)]) | c <- colorSteps(color("Yellow"), color("Blue"), 10) ];
render(hcat(boxes));
----
gives:

